basetypes.images

Class GifTTAA

  • java.lang.Object
    • basetypes.images.GifTTAA
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Processable<ImageTTAA,GifTTAA>, java.lang.Iterable<ImageTTAA>

    public class GifTTAA
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<ImageTTAA>, Processable<ImageTTAA,GifTTAA>
    Basic class for representing animated gif images. Its main elements are three lists: one for the images, one for the delays (per image), and one for the disposal type (per image). This permits inserting new images, for example, and controlling the delay times and transition methods for each frame.
    Author:
    Tristan
